name: UtesFootballAlumniBriefing
0:
”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”
”Alexa, play my Flash Briefing”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des: Want to hear all the ins and out of Utah football through the perspective of athletes who have been there and experienced it? This is the flash briefing for you! We break down upcoming matchups, players to watch and tell stories of the good old days. All from players you know and love! Join us each week to hear what we think you should look out for in the upcoming game, recap highlights and reminiscence about past rivalries and matchups few could ever forget. Join the Utes Football Briefing.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
